Happy International Day of Women and Girls in Science! I’m so proud to celebrate women around the world who are breaking barriers in #STEM – including Betty, a member of the 
@girlsalliance from Kenya who gives girls with disabilities access to #STEM education.

Watch her story: https://t.co/Ocq7bH6yRf

I was thrilled to recently sit down with some inspiring women—
@AngieMartinez, @KellyRowland, Tina Lawson, @WinnieHarlow and @HerMusic—to discuss themes in my book, #TheLightWeCarry.

Watch the conversation tonight on @REVOLTtv. https://t.co/KfIlKpFGJs
